us to strip.

464
00:22:38,750 --> 00:22:39,875
[AINS]
Uh...

465
00:22:39,958 --> 00:22:42,333
[DEMIURGE]
My deepest apologies, Lord Ains!

466
00:22:42,416 --> 00:22:44,250
The overseer of the guardians...

467
00:22:44,333 --> 00:22:46,333
How dare she speak
in such a manner.

468
00:22:46,416 --> 00:22:47,416
I'll tell her to stop at once!

469
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:48,916
[AINS]
No! Well. I mean.

470
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:51,000
Albedo already
has enough stress.

471
00:22:51,083 --> 00:22:53,291
This is her time to
cut loose and relax.

472
00:22:53,375 --> 00:22:54,500
[DEMIURGE]
Of course, understood.

473
00:22:54,583 --> 00:22:56,208
[rumbling]

474
00:22:56,291 --> 00:22:58,000
[AURA]
Whoa, hey, what're you doing?

475
00:22:58,083 --> 00:23:00,541
You can't just jump in
without rinsing off!

476
00:23:02,916 --> 00:23:06,125
[AURA] What the...?
Is that stone lion moving?

477
00:23:06,208 --> 00:23:08,500
[LUCIFER] Those who lack
bathing manners have no right

478
00:23:08,583 --> 00:23:10,166
