479
00:23:10,250 --> 00:23:11,333
[LADIES scream]

480
00:23:11,416 --> 00:23:12,750
[LUCIFER]
Suffer your divine punishment!

481
00:23:12,833 --> 00:23:14,416
[COCYTUS]
A guardian of the baths?

482
00:23:14,500 --> 00:23:17,541
I had no idea such
a creature existed.

483
00:23:17,625 --> 00:23:19,791
[AINS] They don't.
That's Lucifer's voice!

484
00:23:19,875 --> 00:23:21,291
It's his doing!

485
00:23:21,375 --> 00:23:23,208
[DEMIURGE]
The supreme being?

486
00:23:23,291 --> 00:23:24,791
[SHALLTEAR]
I can't even crack it!

487
00:23:24,875 --> 00:23:27,166
This is no normal golem! Albedo!

488
00:23:27,250 --> 00:23:30,750
